          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "testimonial_content": "<p>I had my very first bridal fitting with made with love and it was such a lovely experience! Ella made me feel so comfortable and was so attentive. Her kindness made the whole appointment so special to me and my guests that came along. The gowns are absolutely stunning and definitely felt like a princess on the day. I can’t recommend them highly enough.</p>",
